{"tid":422030,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"索款2萬換取不追究案件　男警涉勒索盜竊被捕","createTime":"2017-10-02T17:14:18.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-03T00:12:03.000Z","uid":5195,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"150c687099318b88faff2f41cebbdba104b290d8","tid":422030,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T17:14:18.000Z","msg":"一名49歲姓張男警員，早前疑向一名男子聲稱他涉及一宗刑事案件，要求事主給予2萬港元，以換取不追究該案件，並相約事主於7月13日在港鐵太子站會面，事主交出1萬港元。事主其後感到可疑，於是向警方報案。<br />\n<br />\n警方深入調查後，昨日（2日）在機場將涉案男警拘捕，涉嫌勒索及盜竊，同時已將他停職。<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">警方發言人表示，非常重視人員的操守，任何人員干犯違法行為，警隊絕不容忍和姑息，定必嚴正處理，進行刑事調查及紀律覆檢。</span>"},{"pid":"6b0f873e33438ff59bd2e624400e0743f3d9df7c","tid":422030,"uid":44209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T17:16:18.000Z","msg":"兩個on9"},{"pid":"450a0ef77c85bc32c793dc5d6d20bc0ee700649e","tid":422030,"uid":73,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T17:17:00.000Z","msg":"本身條友唔係身有屎點㑹交一萬<br />\n調轉頭勒索返個警員都得啦"},{"pid":"b9c481e4a8917753bd438f5f71043d2dda6e1880","tid":422030,"uid":6347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T17:17:55.000Z","msg":"仲以為冒警<br />\n香港公安 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1094060159c0350dd88fb52df85ed9533cbeb0db","tid":422030,"uid":44358,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T17:18:37.000Z","msg":"當更警 +1<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"72db55d71e86e34181b229b19d6873cf65aefa63","tid":422030,"uid":22974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T17:20:32.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"40c774a04a1aa51737fb10c031a9b70d6c33b45a","tid":422030,"uid":29314,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T17:21:24.000Z","msg":"又黎休班警"},{"pid":"2c40290e40b801441a05e7a50cf6fc2cfe2ead07","tid":422030,"uid":59898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T17:23:52.000Z","msg":"<img 